    "# Fine-Tuning Llama 3.2 3B for Cloud Deployment\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook walks through the process of fine-tuning the `meta-llama/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct` model using QLoRA (4-bit quantization) on a custom dataset. \n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal:** Prepare a model that will be used exclusively through the Hugging Face Inference API, not locally. The final step involves pushing the merged model to the Hugging Face Hub."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 1: Install Required Libraries\n",
    "\n",
    "First, we need to install all the necessary libraries for fine-tuning. This includes `transformers` for model handling, `datasets` for data loading, `peft` for LoRA, `bitsandbytes` for quantization, `accelerate` for hardware optimization, and `trl` for the training loop."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!pip install -q transformers datasets peft bitsandbytes accelerate trl"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 2: Configuration and Hugging Face Login\n",
    "\n",
    "Set up all the necessary configurations, including your Hugging Face credentials, model names, and training hyperparameters. **Remember to replace the placeholder values with your actual information.**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "from huggingface_hub import login\n",
    "\n",
    "# --- Hugging Face Configuration ---"",
    "# (IMPORTANT: Replace with your actual token and username)"",
    "HF_TOKEN = \"hf_your_token_here\"  \n",
    "HF_USERNAME = \"your_username\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# --- Model and Dataset Configuration ---"",
    "DATASET_NAME = f\"{HF_USERNAME}/your_dataset\" # Replace with your dataset path"",
    "BASE_MODEL_NAME = \"meta-llama/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct\""",
    "OUTPUT_MODEL_NAME = \"llama-3.2-3b-coach-assistant\" # Name for your fine-tuned model on the Hub"",
    "\n",
    "# --- Training Configuration ---"",
    "MAX_SEQ_LENGTH = 512"",
    "NUM_EPOCHS = 3"",
    "BATCH_SIZE = 4"",
    "GRADIENT_ACCUMULATION_STEPS = 4"",
    "LEARNING_RATE = 2e-4"",
    "WARMUP_STEPS = 50"",
    "\n",
    "# --- LoRA Configuration ---"",
    "LORA_R = 16"",
    "LORA_ALPHA = 32"",
    "LORA_DROPOUT = 0.05"",
    "\n",
    "# --- Directory for local checkpoints ---"",
    "OUTPUT_DIR = \"./results\""",
    "\n",
    "# --- Login to Hugging Face Hub ---"",
    "print(\"Logging into Hugging Face Hub...\")"",
    "try:"",
    "    login(token=HF_TOKEN)"",
    "    print(\"✅ Successfully logged into Hugging Face Hub\")"",
    "except Exception as e:"",
    "    print(f\"❌ Failed to login: {e}\")"",
    "    print(\"Please check your HF_TOKEN and try again\")""
   ]
  },
